text: Nick Lashaway (March 24, 1988 - May 8, 2016) was an American actor. He was best known for his roles on The X-Files, Girls, and The 40 Year Old Virgin. He appeared in The Last Song. He played Brandon O'Neil in My Soul to Take. Lashaway died in a car crash on May 8, 2016, in Framingham, Massachusetts, aged 28. ==References== ==Other websites== * * Notice of death of Lashaway in Framingham, Massachusetts Category:1988 births Category:2016 deaths Category:Road accident deaths in the United States Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors Category:Actors from Washington, D.C.
